MTU Has 1.5 Billion Euros for Purchases, Boersen-Zeitung Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-04-09T10:05:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/mtu-has-1-5-billion-euros-for-purchases-boersen-zeitung-says.html
MTU Aero Engines Holding AG (MTX)  has as
much as 1.5 billion euros ($2.2 billion) to spend on
acquisitions if the right opportunities arise,  Boersen-Zeitung 
reported today, citing Chief Financial Officer Reiner Winkler.  The company forecasts an increase in sales to 6 billion
euros and that profit will double by 2020, the German newspaper
said, citing an interview with Winkler.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net ;  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net  